Generate an SSL certificate in a keystore

	# create PKSC12 keystore:

	keytool -genkeypair -alias securerest -keyalg RSA -keysize 4096 -storetype PKCS12 -keystore securerest.p12 -validity 3650 -storepass p@ssword

	(Alternate for jks):

	keytool -genkeypair -alias securerest -keyalg RSA -keysize 4096 -storetype JKS -keystore securerest.jks -validity 3650 -storepass p@ssword

	(Convert a JKS keystore into PKCS12):

	keytool -importkeystore -srckeystore securerest.jks -destkeystore securerest.p12 -deststoretype pkcs12


